    <title><literal>SetGlobalVar()</literal></title>

    <indexterm significance="preferred">
      <primary>Dialplan Applications</primary>

      <secondary><code>SetGlobalVar()</code></secondary>
    </indexterm>

    <simpara>Sets the value of a global variable.</simpara>

    <synopsis><command>SetGlobalVar(variable=<replaceable>value</replaceable>)</command></synopsis>

    <simpara>Sets the value of a global variable. If the variable does not
    exist, it is created.</simpara>

    <xi:include href="setglobalvar-help.xml" parse="xml" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" xpointer="xpointer(/note/*)" />

    <important>
      <para>Though it is not noted in the internal help, this application is
      deprecated. See the source code:<programlisting>ast_log(LOG_WARNING, "SetGlobalVar is deprecated.  Please use Set(GLOBAL(%s)=%s) instead.\n", name, stringp);</programlisting></para>
    </important>

